<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🚶 M000 Week 1 — English Worksheet (Beginner)</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Agent Movement · <strong>Course:</strong> Builder Basics · <strong>Level:</strong> Beginner · <strong>Time:</strong> about 30 minutes</p>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Predict 🔮</h2>
<p>Read the steps. Circle your answer.</p>
<pre><code>move forward
move forward
</code></pre>
<p><strong>How many steps does the agent take? Circle one:</strong> 1 · 2 · 3</p>
<p><strong>Where is the agent now? Circle one:</strong> 2 steps ahead · back at the start · up high</p>
<pre><code>move forward
turn right
move forward
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Does the agent walk in a straight line? Circle one:</strong> yes · no</p>
<p><strong>What does <code>turn right</code> change? Circle one:</strong> the way it faces · its height · the block it holds</p>
<hr />
<h2>2 · Find the Difference 🐛</h2>
<p>Clean steps first, then a broken version. Circle the bug.</p>
<p><strong>Pair A</strong> — The agent should walk 3 steps forward.</p>
<pre><code># clean
move forward
move forward
move forward
</code></pre>
<pre><code># buggy
move forward
move forward
</code></pre>
<p><strong>What is wrong? Circle one:</strong> one step missing · one step extra · a wrong turn</p>
<p><strong>Pair B</strong> — The agent should walk forward, then turn right.</p>
<pre><code># clean
move forward
turn right
</code></pre>
<pre><code># buggy
turn right
move forward
</code></pre>
<p><strong>What is wrong? Circle one:</strong> wrong order · a step is missing · an extra turn</p>
<hr />
<h2>3 · Fill the Gap ✏️</h2>
<p>The agent goes forward 2 steps, then <strong>up</strong> 2 blocks. One line is missing.</p>
<pre><code>move forward
move forward
____________
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Which line is missing? Circle one:</strong> move up by 2 · turn right · move forward</p>
<hr />
<h2>4 · Show Your Work 📸🎥</h2>
<p>Switch to your homework world. Move your agent <strong>5 steps forward</strong>, then make it <strong>turn once</strong>.</p>
<p>Record <strong>one video</strong> (a phone is fine). Show two things:</p>
<p><strong>1 · Your code.</strong> Scroll through it. Say what each part does.</p>
<p><strong>2 · Your build.</strong> Point the camera. Name the parts.</p>
<p>Say these out loud, filling in the blanks:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Today I built ______.</p>
<p>I built it using this code: ______.</p>
<p>In this code I used ______.</p>
<p>The hardest part was ______.</p>
<p>That part was hard because ______.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<h3>Submit ✅</h3>
<p>Send this worksheet + your video to teacher on KakaoTalk.</p>
<div class="footer">영어코딩 · <b>english-coding.co.uk</b></div>
</div></body></html>
